lens_registry.v1.json — Schema + Semantics
1. Purpose of this file
Defines:
Canonical lens inventory
Lens selection constraints
Rotation/cooldown enforcement
Arc-based depth progression rules
Phase-sensitive preferences (soft rules)
Used by:
Interpreter (select lens for each configuration)
Editorial planner (avoid repetition across segments/days)
QA (detect illegal reuse / regression)
If missing or invalid → pipeline must fail.

2. High-level shape
{
  "version": "1.0",
  "status": "locked",
  "defaults": { ... },
  "lenses": { ... },
  "rotation_rules": { ... },
  "arc_progression": { ... },
  "phase_preferences": { ... },
  "violation_classes": { ... }
}


